---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import profileImg from "../assets/images/profile.webp";
import SectionHeader from "./SectionHeader.astro";
---

<section id="about" class="section-padding relative" aria-labelledby="about-heading">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">
    <SectionHeader id="about" label="about" />

    <div class="grid items-start gap-12 lg:grid-cols-5 lg:gap-16">
      <div class="flex justify-center lg:col-span-2 lg:justify-start">
        <div
          class="crt-vignette bg-screen-panel border-screen-raised/50 h-64 w-64 overflow-hidden rounded-lg border lg:aspect-square lg:h-auto lg:w-full"
        >
          <Image
            src={profileImg}
            alt="Andrew Marich"
            widths={[256, 512, 1024]}
            sizes="(min-width: 1024px) 512px, 256px"
            class="h-full w-full object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="lg:col-span-3">
        <div class="text-text-muted space-y-5 leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            I'm a full-stack engineer out of Gilbert, Arizona. Grew up in Tucson and got my start in
            <span class="text-text-bright">Finance</span> at the University of Arizona, realized I liked
            building software more than analyzing spreadsheets, and went back for a
            <span class="text-text-bright">Computer Science</span> degree from WGU.
          </p>
          <p>
            These days I split my time between two roles. At
            <span style="color: oklch(64% .204 222);">B1 Marketing Group</span> I'm developing the company's
            software and tooling from the ground up. I'm also CTO and co-founder of
            <span style="color: #8b5cf6;">Balance</span>, a medical billing platform.
          </p>
          <p>
            I'm right at home between the technical and business side of things, and understanding
            what drives each helps me build better products.
          </p>
          <p>
            Outside of work I spend most of my time with my wife, our daughter, and two Labs who
            think they run the house... they're probably right. Big on sushi, hoops, and gaming.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
